{"lemma":"قُبْحِ","slug":"قُبْحِ","root":"ق.ب.ح","root_slug":"ق-ب-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ب-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":16},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35052","n35057"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8F%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%AD%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be ugly, to be vile, to be foul, to be hideous"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be bad, to be evil"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be infamous"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be abominable"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make ugly, make vile, make foul, make hideous"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make bad, make evil"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make infamous"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make abominable"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to treat or worthless or abject"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to reproach with"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of قَبُحَ (qabuḥa, “to be ugly”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ugliness, vileness, foulness, hideousness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"badness, evil"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"infamy"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"abominableness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"vice"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35052","headword_ar":"قَبُحَ","root":"qbH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quboHN","text_ar":"قُبْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) [or this, accord. to the S, seems to be a simple subst.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaboHN","text_ar":"قَبْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabaAHapN","text_ar":"قَبَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qubuwHapN","text_ar":"قُبُوحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qubuwHN","text_ar":"قُبُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qubaAHN","text_ar":"قُبَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a form, and an action, L, and anything, T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, bad, evil, abominable, foul, unseemly, unsightly, ugly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hideous; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasuna","text_ar":"حَسُنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K, TA, &c.) One says of a man,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabuHa wa$aquHa","text_ar":"قَبُحَ وَشَقُحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. using the latter v. as an imitative sequent]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a biAlqabaAHapi waAl$~aqaAHapi","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ بِالقَبَاحَةِ وَالشَّقَاحَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"said, what was bad"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$qH","text_ar":"شقح"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AuqobuHo A_ino kunota qaAbiHFA","text_ar":"اُقْبُحْ اـِنْ كُنْتَ قَابِحًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Be thou bad"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"if thou be desirous of becoming so:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawoqa maA qabuHa","text_ar":"قَوْقَ مَا قَبُحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA huwa biqaAbiHK","text_ar":"مَا هُوَ بِقَابِحٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is not becoming bad"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"will not become bad"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above the degree in which he has become so:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in like manner one says in similar cases. (Lh, L.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taqobaHuwA Alwajoha","text_ar":"لَا تَقْبَحُوا الوَجْهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in a trad., means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Say not ye that the face is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabiyH","text_ar":"قَبِيح"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unseemly, unsightly, ugly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hideous"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; because God formed it: or the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"say not ye"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabaHa A@ll~`hu wajoha fulaAnK","text_ar":"قَبَحَ ا@للّٰهُ وَجْهَ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[expl. in what follows]. (L.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabaHahu A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"قَبَحَهُ ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K, TA, &c., [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qab~aHahu","text_ar":"قَبَّحَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaboHN","text_ar":"قَبْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qubuwHN","text_ar":"قُبُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, L, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God removed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may God remove him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K, &c.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prosperity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from all that is good;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA;) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from success,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the attainment of that which he deserves"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seeks;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see the pass. part. n.;)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like as one does the dog and the pig:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, L, TA:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God drove him away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may God drive him away, like a dog:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God rendered him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may God render him, foul, unseemly, unsightly, ugly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hideous, in form:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see, again, the pass. part. n.:)] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qab~aHahu","text_ar":"قَبَّحَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has a similar, but intensive, signification. (Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaboHFA lahu","text_ar":"قَبْحًا لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[an elliptical expression, a verb and its agent being understood, i. e., with these supplied, ("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God decree"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"removal far from good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cause"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"removal"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. ("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to cleave"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may removal"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"betide him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quboHFA","text_ar":"قُبْحًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A) also, (S,) with damm; (A;) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foulness,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2480},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unseemliness, unsightliness, ugliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hideousness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu wa$uqoHFA","text_ar":"لَهُ وَشُقْحًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quboHFA","text_ar":"قُبْحًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L, K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaboHFA lahu","text_ar":"قَبْحًا لَهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa$aqoHFA","text_ar":"وَشَقْحًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; in which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$qHA","text_ar":"شقحا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [said to be] an imitative sequent. (L, TA: but see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$qH","text_ar":"شقح"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabaHotu","text_ar":"قَبَحْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu wajohahu","text_ar":"لَهُ وَجْهَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [thus,] without teshdeed, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I said to him,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabaHa A@ll~`hu wajohaka","text_ar":"قَبَحَ ا@للّٰهُ وَجْهَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God remove thee far from good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohaka","text_ar":"وَجْهَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafosaka","text_ar":"نَفْسَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the phrase being] from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaboHu","text_ar":"القَبْحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ the removing far [from good, &c.]. ” (AA, L. [See an ex. in a verse cited in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sbH","text_ar":"سبح"},{"kind":"text","text":", conj. 2.])       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabaHa","text_ar":"قَبَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, L, K, TA, [accord. to the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qb~H","text_ar":"قبّح"},{"kind":"text","text":", and so in one of two copies of the A, but the former is the right, as is shown by the form of the aor. in an ex. in the TA,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke"},{"kind":"text","text":"a purulent pustule (in his face, L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that the matter might come forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he squeezed"},{"kind":"text","text":"a purulent pustule"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to express its contents before it was ripe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) and [in like manner]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he broke"},{"kind":"text","text":"an egg, (K,) or anything. (L.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","S","AZ","L","TA","A"]},{"entry_id":"n35057","headword_ar":"قُبْحٌ","root":"qbH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[either an inf. n. or a simple subst.; much used as a simple subst., and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqaAbiHu","text_ar":"مَقَابِحُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v., may be an anomalous pl. thereof, like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHaAsinu","text_ar":"مَحَاسِنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to be of its contr."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HusonN","text_ar":"حُسْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: see 1, first sentence; and again, in two places, in the latter half."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}